Comment: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.69,0:00:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.98,0:00:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司被甩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.44,0:00:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 繪瑠是這麼報告的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.16,0:00:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}過去跟他說說話會不會好點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.82,0:00:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我覺得先放他一段時間比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.83,0:00:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}康孝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.70,0:01:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看來受傷很重
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.29,0:01:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}別胡鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.75,0:01:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我只是想要讓司打起精神…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.42,0:01:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 你真的向艾拉告白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.65,0:01:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.82,0:01:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}忽然把你叫出來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.69,0:01:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你… 那個… 沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}另外
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.20,0:01:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司真的向你告白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.58,0:01:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且我聽說你拒絕他了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.84,0:01:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎怎…怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.17,0:01:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我我我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.26,0:02:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被告 告 告白了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你完全看起來不像沒事的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我突然就被告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.45,0:03:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}腦子裡跳出了許多想法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}完全不知道該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}順勢就告訴他不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:04:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之後司就一直那個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.67,0:04:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算我向他搭話似乎也聽不見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.93,0:04:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他那樣子不管誰去搭話都一樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.47,0:04:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這不是艾拉需要在意的事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}該說司最近有些得意忘形吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}會變成這樣肯定大概就是他的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他一定是不會看氣氛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.95,0:04:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}突然就跑出來告白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我和司在嘉年華會場上走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看吧果然是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}連好好保護女生都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一點用都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是他非常拚命地找我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最後找到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛 這是理所應當的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之後就開始放煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們一起牽著手看煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.56,0:04:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在那時候牽手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還不錯…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然後順著話題就被抱住了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:05:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那可真是激情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然後就被告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.53,0:05:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這一點都不浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}肯定要拒絕的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也會那麼做的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你臉好紅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我傷害了司
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉想怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.35,0:05:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果是滿會怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.01,0:05:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我覺得就算你問她也沒什麼意義
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}滿又沒有被人告白過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}夠了 別在那多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.73,0:05:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在司面前你還能像以前一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想兩個人都應該先冷靜下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.50,0:05:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要試試跟司分開過幾天嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.79,0:06:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那樣的話你也可以好好考慮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對他到底是怎樣的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.05,0:06:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}分開…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.72,0:06:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}具體怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…現在正在想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}原來你沒有計劃啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天的目標需要小心一點比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}持有者引起過暴力事件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是有前科的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}話說…你知道司向艾拉告白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼！ 真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.99,0:06:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}繪瑠告訴我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼時候的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司求婚時說了些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 不是求婚 是告白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.42,0:06:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那兩個傢伙 進展到什麼程度了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你說進展…是指的什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大概…知道你想說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.56,0:06:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}結果呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:06:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉似乎拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拒絕了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也沒有想到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你的表情很可怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}閉嘴
Comment: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}聽懂了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.07,0:07:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要是擅自動房間的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可不會輕易饒過你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}塞克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要是司做了任何一點可疑的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就把他趕出房間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吶吶 司
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}滿的內衣放在這邊的抽屜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那邊是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.92,0:07:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你告訴他幹嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.26,0:07:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 為什麼我和司住一間房
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}現在的司氣氛那麼沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可不想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.47,0:07:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}暫且忍一忍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}男生和女生換一下房間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要和繪瑠一起照顧艾拉才行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.81,0:07:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}安慰司就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.52,0:07:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用做到那種程度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你打算消沉到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.24,0:07:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}給我爽快點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被甩掉而已有什麼大不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.09,0:08:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}反正不理你 你也只會坐在那裡什麼都不吃發呆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在我的房間餓死了 我可受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我怎麼覺得一晚上不吃不喝也死不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.43,0:08:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你說了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.27,0:08:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吃吧 趁著還沒有涼快點吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哼 我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}來 艾拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}趁著還沒有涼趕快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可是努力了一把
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快點吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比…比起這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼你給我穿這件衣服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉拉竟然會來我的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.47,0:08:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}夢想成真了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:08:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今晚太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}完全冷靜不下來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.31,0:09:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}塞克 太不像話了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不認真工作卻一心搞職場戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}區區一個新人太囂張了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這是現在還把自己當學生的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我無話可說…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.13,0:09:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道你很受打擊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你要把工作和私生活分開
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}現在像你這樣的廢柴 去回收和家人一樣的吉芙提爾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.34,0:09:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}別人會怎麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.43,0:09:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我跟你說過我爸爸變成遊蕩者的事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我眼睜睜的失去父親 變成孤零零一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然香月姐來看過我很多次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:10:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我覺得過意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就對她說了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}「你不用再來了」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為吉芙提爾和持有者提供心靈依靠是終端服務的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我雖然不能代替你的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.34,0:10:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是至少能陪你說說話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在你振作起來之前希望你讓我這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.52,0:10:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要不然我沒辦法面對你的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.69,0:10:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我看到那樣的香月姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才想加入終端服務
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我為自己在這裡工作感到驕傲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以如果你在這裡混日子的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.16,0:10:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我饒不了你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.41,0:10:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝你關心我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.13,0:10:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哼 我只是作為一個前輩指導你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.13,0:11:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}告白之後後悔了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然被拒絕了 但是對艾拉的感情不會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.48,0:11:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你還挺執著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我覺得你這點很帥…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為…為什麼我剛才
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.53,0:11:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}話說你真的懂我在說什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}懂的話就別在那裡發呆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好好想想今後怎麼和艾拉接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.83,0:11:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\blur2}真的是愛管閒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你知道什麼了說出來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我會聽著的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉拉 今晚不會讓你睡的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.55,0:11:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}來開睡衣派對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好吧 好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.89,0:11:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…滿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.22,0:11:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}說起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等下就會來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比起那個 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為了艾拉拉我準備了這麼多的睡衣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.27,0:11:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}從哪個開始穿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.36,0:11:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吶 從哪個開始？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.82,0:12:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}滿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}睡相
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.01,0:12:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被看見了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.22,0:12:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可惡 沒想到竟然睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不快點準備的話要遲到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.77,0:12:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼不早點叫我起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}總覺得…有點怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.60,0:12:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你這話什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我沒有在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.11,0:12:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這不是我該在意的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不不 這是誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.33,0:12:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對 我們並沒有做什麼下流的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒關係 司和滿很般配的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:12:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}糟糕 要趕快追上去才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}振作一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.14,0:13:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}解開了誤會真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我太衝動弄錯了 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.31,0:13:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 要怪也怪我沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}別不說話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.49,0:13:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好不容易有這個機會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好好聊一下怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.04,0:13:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還是不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.67,0:13:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…司
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.72,0:13:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.39,0:13:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我那時候拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是想好好考慮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再給我一些時間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.94,0:14:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}當然沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.31,0:14:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是無論艾拉作何決斷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.23,0:14:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請至少讓我繼續做你的搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你有什麼在意的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老爺子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你覺得戀愛是不是氣勢也很重要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是指艾拉的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我讓那孩子好好考慮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.85,0:14:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但這樣真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這種事花費太多時間的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.35,0:14:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}會向著壞的方向考慮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.32,0:14:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不知道…究竟怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:14:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:14:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:15:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那我們一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.47,0:15:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天是什麼茶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.94,0:15:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.37,0:15:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你實際上是怎麼看待司的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.09,0:15:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼司總是在笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.59,0:15:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一開始讓我在意的是這件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之前滿不是也說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:16:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司可能是因為悲傷而笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不想讓他有那樣的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}總想著要幫他些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.86,0:16:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是去遊樂園的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}從中途心就怦怦地跳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.25,0:16:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}從那以後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一想到司的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我心裡就充滿緊張和悸動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒辦法用語言來形容
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.10,0:16:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是嗎是嗎 果然是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已經得到答案了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.35,0:16:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你自己也清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.77,0:16:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}答案…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.03,0:16:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 答案早已經有了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:16:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然 那就趕快去和司說…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.49,0:17:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\blur2}我要離開司
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.37,0:17:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等下 你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我覺得這樣做對彼此都很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.80,0:17:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等等 不對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.39,0:17:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣的話我就跟你明說了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.72,0:17:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你感覺到的這種悸動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是戀愛 是戀愛的心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}戀愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.94,0:17:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以根本不需要離開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.94,0:17:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果是那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.11,0:17:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我更要遠離司了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.16,0:17:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不懂 我不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}告訴我為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.29,0:17:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼樣才能得出這樣的結論
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為…一個月
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為我只剩下大概一個月的壽命了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.81,0:18:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喲 你居然沒喝醉真是罕見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.36,0:18:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}別那麼瞪著我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要是嫌我礙事的話 我會自動消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.74,0:18:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你是不是煽動司了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}煽動什麼的 太失禮了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.37,0:18:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他只是自己想清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.45,0:18:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}像個男人一樣表達出自己的心意而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.33,0:18:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}結果就是那個德行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.79,0:18:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他們倆好不容易才合拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那麼你是打算干涉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然至今一直在逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.76,0:18:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只有這種時候才會裝得像個前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.73,0:18:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我這人對於可愛的後輩的事情可是一清二楚的喲
Comment: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.24,0:19:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}滿？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在這種地方幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.96,0:19:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉壽命的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.88,0:19:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你什麼時候知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.64,0:19:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.23,0:19:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是最近
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我明明什麼都不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}卻對你和艾拉儘說些自作聰明的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.37,0:19:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.12,0:19:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明應該在工作上已經適應了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你說是最近才知道壽命的事的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.55,0:20:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是在告白之前 還是之後
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.51,0:20:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那麼 你是明明知道還去告白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.30,0:20:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你做了這個工作以後 到底都看到了些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.89,0:20:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}分手是注定的 而你為什麼還要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你到底想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.14,0:20:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想創造和艾拉在一起的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.86,0:20:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想為艾拉創造回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.15,0:20:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.15,0:20:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算如此 我也想為她做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你想要做的是非常痛苦的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不可能會有什麼好結果的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.08,0:20:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算如此 你也能毫不退縮地面對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.29,0:20:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我…我在爸爸的那時候逃避了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.05,0:20:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒能面對他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.38,0:20:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因此傷害了很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.89,0:20:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你能夠負責到底嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.47,0:20:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我已經決定 要一直做艾拉的搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.48,0:20:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}直到最後的一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.44,0:21:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}責任的意義 你明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.07,0:21:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.82,0:21:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你和那時的我完全不一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.71,0:21:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是這樣我才說外行完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.38,0:21:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你…你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.34,0:21:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我在說你是個無藥可救的戀愛新手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.72,0:21:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以 我就稍微支持一下你們的戀愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.93,0:21:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好好謝謝我吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.40,0:21:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.29,0:21:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香月姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.12,0:21:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.16,0:21:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼你會在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.04,0:21:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你來得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.75,0:22:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我有話對你說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.30,0:22:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.80,0:22:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.30,0:22:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我被香月叫了過來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.27,0:22:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}從今天起 你們兩個解除搭檔關係
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.94,0:22:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.56,0:22:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.69,0:22:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒聽清楚嗎 解除搭檔關係
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
